	<div class="contentwide">
		<h2>Summary:</h2><div class="infobox">Depending on how positive or negative your overall Health level is, there are different effects on your people as a whole. Negative Health causes penalties, which get larger the worse Health gets. Similarly, positive Health gives bonuses, which get larger the better Health gets.<br /><br />[ICON_BULLET]From -20 to -70, Production is penalized -1% per point (up to -50%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From -15 to -65, enemy Covert Ops Intrigue is increased +2% per point (up to +100%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From -10 to -60, Science is penalized -1% per point (up to -50%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From -5 to -55, Culture is penalized -1% per point (up to -50%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From 0 to -50, Outpost Growth is penalized -2% per point (up to -100%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From 0 to -50, City Growth is penalized -2% per point (up to -100%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From 1 to 5, nothing happens.<br />[ICON_BULLET]From 5 to 25, Production bonus +1% per point (up to +20%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From 10 to 30, enemy Covert Ops Intrigue is decreased -2% per point (up to -40%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From 15 to 35, Science bonus +1% per point (up to +20%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From 20 to 40, Culture bonus +1% per point (up to +20%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From 25 to 45, City Growth bonus +1% per point (up to +20%)<br />[ICON_BULLET]From 25 to 45, Outpost Growth bonus +2% per point (up to +40%)</div>
